OL,4,Care trained to spot domestic abuse
OL,5,Csigns
OL,7,FFear Fear estimates that one in four
OL,8,Fwomen experience domestic abuse and
OL,9,Fone in six to seven men.
OL,11,F'Comb Together' will soon be rolled
OL,12,Fout to another 20 barbers, hair and
OL,13,Fbeauty salons across the West Country.
OL,15,FJoshua Frantz-Morgans, who is an
OL,16,Findependent domestic violence advisor
OL,17,Ffor the charity, said: "We also want
OL,18,Fto make sure men have safe spaces too.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
