OL,3,CInside the salon where hairdressers
OL,4,Care trained to spot domestic abuse
OL,5,Csigns
OL,7,FShe said: "When you're seeing a guests
OL,8,Fthat you've seen multiple times, they
OL,9,Fcan become very comfortable and you
OL,10,Fcan build a nice relationship with
OL,11,Fthem.
OL,13,F"They can feel that they can really
OL,14,Flet go and tell you their worries and
OL,15,Fconcerns. I feel like the salon is a
OL,16,Fvery calming, relaxing atmosphere.
OL,18,F"You're not really sat close to people
OL,19,Fso there is a bit more confidentiality
OL,20,Fabout it."
