OL,4,Care trained to spot domestic abuse
OL,5,Csigns
OL,7,FFear Free is a charity working across
OL,8,FDevon and Wiltshire, working to "break
OL,9,Fthe cycle" of domestic abuse, sexual
OL,10,Fviolence and stalking.
OL,12,FThe team supports more than 10,000
OL,13,Fadults and children every year, "not
OL,14,Fonly keep them safe" but help them to
OL,15,Frebuild their lives "free from fear
OL,16,Fand abuse."
OL,18,FIf you or somebody you know is
OL,19,Faffected by domestic abuse, FearFree
OL,20,Fis available to help in the South West.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
